{"tid":440241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘MR.HA派對場地爆發諾如病毒，21人中招！！","createTime":"2017-10-18T14:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T17:58:56.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"950c5237a09c30f179ac6df7fb762d0ee33e25bd","tid":440241,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:35:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171018/photo/bkn-20171018190312089-1018_00822_001_01p.jpg?20171018204602\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171018%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171018190312089-1018_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20171018204602&h=b0e4cd79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n衞生署衞生防護中心今日(18日)公布，正調查觀塘MR.HA一個多用途派對場地爆發的諾如病毒腸胃炎個案。個案涉及21名病人，包括10名為幼童，分別為4男6女，年齡由1至13歲，另有11名成年人，分別為5男6女，年齡由29至40歲。全部病人一直情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171018/bkn-20171018190312089-1018_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171018%2Fbkn-20171018190312089-1018_00822_001.html&d=eHgTl0akRFSu%2Bkp8QTI6lv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ab411b12\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171018/bkn-20171018190312089-1018_00822_001.html</a></div>"},{"pid":"396c628414cf4c42c450d9a9a8abfe3ca19b662f","tid":440241,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:36:14.000Z","msg":"21名病人本月13至18日起出現嘔吐及腹瀉等病徵，其中14人已經求醫，當中一名1歲男童曾到荃灣港安醫院求醫，其糞便樣本經化驗後，證實對諾如病毒呈陽性反應，他現已出院。<br />\n<br />\n該個MR.HA多用途派對場地位於開源道55號開聯工業中心A座，初步調查顯示，所有病人曾於本月14日到該場地參與派對，其中一名幼童於派對前已經出現輕微病徵。衞生防護中心人員已實地視察該場地。<br />\n<br />\nMR.HA員工表示，每次包場活動後都會進行大型清潔，包括消毒及更換波波池內的波波，以確保場地衞生，小朋友入來時都須探熱及消毒雙手，而衞生署職員及醫生視察後，均對衞生情況表示滿意，MR.HA未來會再加強清潔。<br />\n<br />\n該場地佔地1800呎，提供兒童派對包場服務，設施包括益智玩具，有滑梯、波波池及學行車等，可同時容納數十人，今年年頭才開張。"},{"pid":"3635f307b03ec9b96b8a2f32b726efee27c54b95","tid":440241,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:41:20.000Z","msg":"好想玩室內沙灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7b893839c99badb57ee7eadb6b1e639f533fbf","tid":440241,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:41:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"575149df2878c4018e2047335a2975f907d510ef","tid":440241,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:43:16.000Z","msg":"私人波波池都咁 都唔明啲家長會夠膽入商場果啲"},{"pid":"f0d84707d6c96195aebad24f3a5e789cfab9087d","tid":440241,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T15:03:48.000Z","msg":"乜撚野諾如病毒"},{"pid":"8a4afaf3883ac10f27d36a27bdb9057ffe6b3c43","tid":440241,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T15:13:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4e509928dc7b8e06d3021a9b270de0e50fc3ab6","tid":440241,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T15:30:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚野諾如病毒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前叫諾沃克病毒"},{"pid":"6a79fc6e3693c6a0186cfe2ddab2b2acc834a02d","tid":440241,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T15:57:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e94d5e85ba9b28c3c74a9aaeed8880f7cefe93a","tid":440241,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:02:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一講起毒，就諗起之前有段片，係貓叉master用arch + kvm qemu + windows打機的片，雖然睇唔到正面，見到佢個側面真係毒到出汁，同金鐘海富雞翼毒男有得揮</blockquote><br />\n又想引戰... 完啦好嗎？"},{"pid":"b7742b2213684a53157ef14235fc960876eda788","tid":440241,"uid":54452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乜撚野諾如病毒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前叫諾沃克病毒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都諗緊諾如病毒係乜撚"},{"pid":"203b77a35aaf2e51c6038cdf4da5a449f5eb16ff","tid":440241,"uid":40337,"like":0,"d